  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1-4 PLAYER ONLINE CO-OP HOLY BRETHREN</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HOLY PURGE is a co-op exorcist horror survival game for up to 4 players.</strong><br><br>Play as Holy Priests and work together to exorcise evil.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 unique exorcism area maps.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f59d6eaf703eb9c80f25094c7d24377c.avif?t=1761870076\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras_big/f59d6eaf703eb9c80f25094c7d24377c.avif?t=1761870076 width=1560 height=370 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BIBLE CAMP MAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/a1e46f55a650548bc7f5f9b4061cd4fa.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Investigate a bible camp for missing children and repel flying demons who possess them.</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VILLAGE MAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c1a7df99ed6a1a4b3102489fd5f9c2c2.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c1a7df99ed6a1a4b3102489fd5f9c2c2.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c1a7df99ed6a1a4b3102489fd5f9c2c2.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete the ritual and cleanse a plague befalling a medieval village.</strong>Collect ritual items to reverse a witch spell and defend yourselves using holy crosses, silver, and fire torches against werewolves and demons.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXORCIST MAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c5da9053cad356c5d2fce5972e1745aa.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c5da9053cad356c5d2fce5972e1745aa.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c5da9053cad356c5d2fce5972e1745aa.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perform an exorcism on a woman possessed by a demon.</strong>Find demonic spirits lurking within a house. Use items to banish these spirits and cleanse the house to weaken the grip on a possessed woman.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f16a345afac648d60bf42f3e99361463.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f16a345afac648d60bf42f3e99361463.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f16a345afac648d60bf42f3e99361463.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Exorcise a possessed daughter and bring her back to life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f052bd7af659c8d8d86c1567895c376a.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f052bd7af659c8d8d86c1567895c376a.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f052bd7af659c8d8d86c1567895c376a.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Work together with your fellow brethren and overcome an ancient evil spirit.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPLAY-ABILITY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doors, ritual Items and collectibles are randomized.<br>Explore each map background lore by reading all notes and cassette messages.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIFFICULTY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay maps with increased difficulty for an increasingly terrifying experience</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SINGLE PLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For hardcore players only. Do it all by yourself. For those who possess the strongest of faith, and therefore the ability to take on the evil alone.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WARNING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains flashing lights that may make it unsuitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy or other photosensitive conditions. Player discretion is advised.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1-4 PLAYER ONLINE CO-OP HOLY BRETHREN</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HOLY PURGE is a co-op exorcist horror survival game for up to 4 players.</strong><br><br>Play as Holy Priests and work together to exorcise evil.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 unique exorcism area maps.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f59d6eaf703eb9c80f25094c7d24377c.avif?t=1761870076\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras_big/f59d6eaf703eb9c80f25094c7d24377c.avif?t=1761870076 width=1560 height=370 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BIBLE CAMP MAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/a1e46f55a650548bc7f5f9b4061cd4fa.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Investigate a bible camp for missing children and repel flying demons who possess them.</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VILLAGE MAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c1a7df99ed6a1a4b3102489fd5f9c2c2.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c1a7df99ed6a1a4b3102489fd5f9c2c2.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c1a7df99ed6a1a4b3102489fd5f9c2c2.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Co